title: Current Prices Basic Commodities, Regions, Philippines, 2009
name: Current Prices Basic Commodities, Regions, Philippines, 2009
description: This data comes from the Department of Trade and Industry of the Philippines. The data shows the current prices of basic commodities in seven regions of the Philippines as of August 24-28, 2009. Data was uploaded into Geocommons as shp, dbf, and shx files.

author.source: Department of Trade and Industry - Philippines
